madagascar is a 2005 american computer-animated comedy film produced by dreamworks animation and released to theaters on may 27 , 2005 . the film tells the story of four animals from the central park zoo who unexpectedly find themselves stranded on the island of madagascar . it features the voices of ben stiller , chris rock , david schwimmer , and jada pinkett smith , with sacha baron cohen , cedric the entertainer , and andy richter voicing secondary characters . despite its mixed critical reception , it was a success at the box office . the film launched a franchise with a series of films , including the sequel madagascar : escape 2 africa in 2008 and another film madagascar 3 : europe 's most wanted in 2012 . a spin-off featuring the series ' penguin characters , penguins of madagascar , was released on november 26 , 2014 .